#: config.inc.php:78
#, php-format
msgid "Test email to %s"
msgstr "Email de test à %s"

#: config.inc.php:80
msgid "This is a test email generated by the Email SMTP RosarioSIS plugin."
msgstr ""
"Ceci est un email de test généré par le pluign Email SMTP pour RosarioSIS."

#: config.inc.php:142
#, php-format
msgid "Email SMTP %s"
msgstr "Email SMTP %s"

#: config.inc.php:149
msgid ""
"If you are sending using an email provider (Gmail, Yahoo, Hotmail, Outlook."
"com, etc) this setting should be your email address for this account."
msgstr ""
"Si vous envoyez depuis un fournisseur d'email (Gmail, Yahoo, Hotmail, "
"Outlook.com, etc), ce devrait être l'adresse email de votre compte."

#: config.inc.php:156
msgid "From Email"
msgstr "Email de"

#: config.inc.php:163
#, php-format
msgid ""
"You can specify the name that emails should be sent from. If you leave this "
"blank, the emails will be sent from %s."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez spécifier le nom depuis lequel les emails devraient être envoyé. "
"Si vous laissez le champ vide, les emails seront envoyé depuis %s."

#: config.inc.php:170
msgid "From Name"
msgstr "Nom de"

#: config.inc.php:179
msgid "SMTP Host"
msgstr "Serveur SMTP"

#: config.inc.php:188
msgid "SMTP Port"
msgstr "Port SMTP"

#: config.inc.php:202
msgid "Encryption"
msgstr "Chiffrage"

#: config.inc.php:229
msgid ""
"If you are sending more than 50 emails at once and receive an SMTP error, "
"adding a pause between each email may help."
msgstr ""
"Si vous envoyez plus de 50 emails à la fois et recevez une erreur SMTP, "
"ajouter une pause entre chaque email peut aider."

#: config.inc.php:236
msgid "Pause between each email (seconds)"
msgstr "Pause entre chaque email (secondes)"

#: config.inc.php:244
msgid "Send a test email To"
msgstr "Envoyer un email de test à"

#: config.inc.php:247
msgid "Send Test"
msgstr "Envoyer le test"

